A vast library with towering shelves stretching into shadows, where instead of books, thousands of glowing amber document cards float in organized columns, some cards drifting through the air following luminous golden threads that connect them like a web. In the foreground, an antique brass mechanical device with multiple spinning rings and rotating discs acts as a sorting mechanism, with streams of tiny illuminated papers flowing through it. The scene is lit by warm gaslight sconces casting dramatic shadows, with dust motes sparkling in the beams. Sepia and bronze tones dominate, with aged wood textures and ornate Victorian metalwork details throughout. Vintage steampunk aesthetic with daguerreotype-style vignetting at the edges.
